{
  "stem": "5644.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because we did arranged to go out.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 93,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And about three, three, three flats further and one of-- inside of a-- of a-- of a--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Not corridor.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 94,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But inside the entrance, the woman will wait for the child to be delivered.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 95,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The nanny--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 96,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I know the name very well, but I wouldn't like to mention the name.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 97,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 98,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Every one of them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 99,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But they had been paid for it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, when I went there, when we went out, we start by providing a little incident where one boy start to run towards the place.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we ran after him screaming, stop, stop, stop, to the boy.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we go next to the entrance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 100,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We're blocking the entrance completely.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 101,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "With body-- with body power.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 102,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You can't go in, and you can't go out.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 103,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, with our-- 50 people.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 104,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And the entrance is about three foot, four foot wide.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the entrance is about 15.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But this is closed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Only three, four foot to walk in and walk out of the place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 105,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was-- that's how that was built there in Poland before the war-- or in Europe.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we blocked completely.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I took out the child.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Give it to the lady.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "She went to the-- to a-- one of the passengers there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 106,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And she start to ask people for a name which is not existent but with the child in the hand.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We moved away.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And about 5, 10 minutes later, by her spending the time of asking for someone who does not exist there, she walked up with the child.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 107,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So there wasn't anything suspicious that you're walking out with the child.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She did have everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Her brother was a policeman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 108,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A Christian policeman.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 109,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So all the correct papers were available.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 110,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Everything she did have for her.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 111,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
